<subSubSection id="E73F6692E92258931C0D7523906BDD00" pageId="null" pageNumber="152" type="description">
<paragraph id="4C74BE9BFC811364A9C3B93210554BDA" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="BAE60428F0E916EB79FC9F9A8C680CAB" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Lycopus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="null" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="europaeus">
<emphasis id="03FF80BFEAF7E83B0ED7A7DA23804C87" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<authorityName id="490ABE7309D12E5C1D44D70B465C3179" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">L.</authorityName>
europaeus
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="A6F25DCA679D5DCA7AF7B9AE9AF31041" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<normalizedToken id="FB85C23463D153C16FBEA402BDDE4A59" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
oval, 2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E9D35A7A4E2DAA840090AA5A6A39BEB3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">3mal so lang wie breit, beiderseits dicht und anliegend behaart</emphasis>
(Haare bis 1 mm lang); Haare auf den 
<normalizedToken id="8EA8D4CDE653C40C89CDB93A81A0EFB2" originalValue="Kelchzähnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Kelchzaehnen</normalizedToken>
0,5-1,2 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="C936204FE93004DE6598AB3847070132" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer und 
<normalizedToken id="976AB83E12BC7CF26A2D38E7E0A779BB" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">frueher</normalizedToken>
Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C88A57208FB948DCC3A1254BDE3F421E" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="340EDA91D88749AA0B7D179E1254B722" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B5D6D29953246E2F8813295C8641C104" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="6C37F1A9E7F5ACA32C7D4DE7B23ACCE9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="176B549CE9F3F7D249AC5F376B903484" class="Arachnida" family="Thomisidae" genus="Lycopus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="null" pageNumber="152" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="europaeus">
<emphasis id="0575646F5050EF48DFFCC9682CD91894" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<authorityName id="A884E57D44BAC62B2822851174D2F2FC" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">L.</authorityName>
europaeus
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D146A26C76C4E0BD397C4EC2FA1A2D93" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="89E703317A24F4AEAB06D0115B18DAF6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="B986CABEB2CA0CB0AB8DBD09C2AD46F4" originalValue="Südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="0B6D2852F705AC0C54D6BEF8B386745E" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="152">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zu den Alpen und Karpaten. - Im Gebiet: Gegend des Genfersees, Rheintal (Liechtenstein), Puschlav, Veltlin, Vintschgau (Naturns, Meran).
</paragraph>
